Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.15,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 心情也变得超级恬静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.08,0:00:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么十分在意的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？阿鲁？我既没有在想阿鲁也没有在意阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}注：日语「有吗」与「阿鲁」发音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么都没在想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级纯情少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 送走炎热的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯渐渐染上了秋天的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是爱丽丝成为正式领航员之后的第一个营业日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 在开始共同练习之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华提议去看看她的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.11,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那份 赏月之夜的心动…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员小姐又很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那是叹息桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}Ponte dei Sospiri：叹息桥建于1603年 因桥上死囚的\N叹息声而得名 据说恋人们在桥下接吻就可以天长地久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 导游手册上写着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在正在前往的 就是叹息桥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美得让人叹息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 名字的由来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前在地球的杜卡雷宫接受了判决的死囚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}杜卡雷宫：古代威尼斯共和国总督的政厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在经过这座桥的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会深深叹一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这次来对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 她怎么这么紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看起来浑身僵硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真的非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们一定还会再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢二位的惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来客人是很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 请忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被爱丽丝发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级注意到了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我们偶然路过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 偶然看到了爱丽丝的工作情形…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来二位刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我的工作啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊…你看 不是还算可以的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 倒划着去追踪猫咪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还完美地继承了雅典娜前辈的周到服务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们从那里就开始看了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷看超级禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…那之外就完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位想说什么就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像玩具机器人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀僵硬得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有时间让你沮丧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你已经是正式领航员啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚去赏月如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赏月？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且今天天气不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮一定很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赏月…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 还是第一次赏月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在AQUA没有这种习俗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在赏月的时候要有团子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是模仿地球的月亮做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次就吃了两个 你好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就吃四个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁…禁止吃着碗里的想着锅里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈你超级律人不律己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆不隆咚的肚子～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长圆不隆咚的肚子可不是月见团子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是邮递员大叔推荐给我的黑米茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个季节喝热饮真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 阿鲁好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 为什么阿鲁他要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们三个人赏月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说起和星球有关的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就得叫阿鲁来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会告诉我们很多事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你那是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为上次看流星雨小后辈你不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才特地叫阿鲁过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去接他过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他八成又是在加班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能迷路了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华前辈 超级可爱的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天邀我赏月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样看着月亮 我感觉轻松了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 我感觉能像月亮一样圆满地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更好地完成自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 再来一杯茶如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？嘛社长不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我加班做得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 工作狂禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀…真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 不过多亏我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能独占这深夜的幽静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华小姐 危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 蓝华小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还…还好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么是阿鲁你道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我太重了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好城里的井都是已经废弃了的枯井
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不至于淹死…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是麻烦了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在还未启用水道之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个广场都设置了井口收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用以解决生活用水问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天早晚这里都挤满了来打水的夫人们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如人们说的 是井边会议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小后辈带来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社长你在听我说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把·小·后·辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带·过·来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你也跟着跳下来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 嘛社长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上去把小后辈叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又跑回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说嘛社长啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 嘛社长还是猫baby啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 嘛社长是能够理解人类语言的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色的水星猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会！把小后辈…叫来…的…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之现在我们全靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 就是那样 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应不应该抱着期待呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点悬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果变成诡异的赏月了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮为什么会绕着AQUA转呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为相互吸引的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与相互远离的力量同时作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我说过的相互吸引的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和圆周运动产生的离心力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形成了微妙的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 月亮既无法靠近 也无法远离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕着AQUA在转动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像某人一样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外侧的月亮被利用于宇宙空间站等等领域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能在真空中完成的科学实验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矿物资源的开采
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球的月亮上的陨石坑被比喻为各种形状哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如有着巨螯的螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在编织的老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狮子 女性的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿饼的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到兔子我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙空间站的兔子薄饼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那个很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想吃吃看 前些天就邮购了一些来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说还会附赠赞美月亮的明信片套装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都等得不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之那种的全部禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井底下还真黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你怕黑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力调节员一般都是在黑漆漆的地方工作的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛在晚上也能看清东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时虽然阳光无法进入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过地下世界的照明设备非常齐全…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁君不用怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心 有大姐姐陪着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月亮变成两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内侧的月亮体积大概是外侧月亮的1.8倍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在AQUA的静止轨道内转动着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8小时以内就能绕着AQUA转动一周的内侧月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是在AQUA上空5900公里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个非常近的轨道内转动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个距离跟地球与月球的距离比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有其65分之1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过接近的小小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了太多AQUA的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再过不久 一定会粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到AQUA影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像只有月亮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对AQUA来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最最接近不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA本身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也被月亮影响着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪费掉了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝…蓝华小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪费掉什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.36,0:20:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 还好找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你居然掉到那里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是对救命恩人说的话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感谢过嘛社长了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从「浪费掉了啦」那个时候哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 浪费掉什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产…产生离心力的方法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果害怕靠近而犹豫不前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子就会饿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是产生引力的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 什么东西让人害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿…阿鲁的大叔用语让人害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 什么东西浪费掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}你是明知故问对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 虽然这是心血来潮的赏月大会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大家都找回了平时的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就变成了一个非常开心的秋夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐 月亮除了有引力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还拥有别的美好的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年秋天我也想参加赏月大会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在激情燃烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.10,0:24:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像小后辈一样～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝很有活力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 瞬息万变的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:08.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}憶えていますか？ あの日を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:18.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ふと感じた ときめきを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:29.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}蒼い日差し浴びて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}風を切る君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:40.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}見とれてると 目が合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}笑顔こぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:52.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}まるで スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:58.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an7}鮮やかに 回り出した日々
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつも いつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:08.95,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}愛が満ちていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:13.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}きっと スピラーレ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:22.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}あたたかな 毎日を重ねたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:31.36,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}いつの間にか 遠くに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:36.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}来ていたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:08.92,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:18.91,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:29.04,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:33.44,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:40.17,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.89,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:52.01,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:58.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}炫目光芒中 崭露头角的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.31,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}永远地 充满
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:08.95,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}让人陶醉的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:13.22,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一定如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:22.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}每个温暖的 日子往复着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:31.36,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不经意间 从那远方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:36.06,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:39.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}金の波 岸辺に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:45.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,1000)}あこがれ目覚めるの 朝に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:59.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰かのことを強く思う時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:08.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}かかげた手のひらに愛がとまる
